# H. Monorepo Rules

## [STRICT] Purpose
- Define clear boundaries and efficient CI for multi-app/package repos.

## [STRICT] Triggers

### GEN_MONO_RULES
- Role: Generate monorepo rules and tasks

### MONO_APPS_PACKAGES
- Role: Enforce `apps/` vs `packages/` separation and ownership

### MONO_SHARED_CONFIGS
- Role: Centralize lint/build/test configs in `packages/config/`

### MONO_AFFECTED_CI
- Role: Configure CI to run affected-only builds/tests

